<title>CANADA: Four Seasons to offer more voting shares.</title>
<headline>Four Seasons to offer more voting shares.</headline>
<dateline>TORONTO 1997-01-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Four Seasons Hotels Inc said on Friday that it filed a preliminary short-form prospectus with securities regulators in Canada and the United States for an offering of additional limited voting shares.</p>
<p>The proposed issue was being underwritten by Morgan Stanley Canada Ltd, Goldman, Sachs and Co and Salomon Brothers Inc, with proceeds used mainly to reduce corporate debt, Four Seasons said.</p>
<p>It said the limited shares could not be sold or bought before the registration statement became effective in the United States or before a receipt for the final short-form prospectus was obtained in Canada.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8100))</p>
